OL,3,CThe campaign urging big brands to
OL,4,C'Think North'
OL,6,FITV News Granada Reports journalist
OL,7,FJahmal Williams-Thomas spoke to those
OL,8,Finvolved in 'Think North'.
OL,10,FA campaign urging big brands to work
OL,11,Fwith Northern creatives has been
OL,12,Flaunched in the North West.
OL,14,F'Think North' is celebrating
OL,15,FManchester and the wider Northern
OL,16,Fcreative scene and pushing for greater
OL,17,Fvisibility and investment in Northern
OL,18,Ftalent.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/8
