CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1779829869
OL,3,CThe campaign urging big brands to
OL,4,C'Think North'
OL,6,FThe project - started by creative
OL,7,Fcommunity builder 'HEADS' and Jack Fox
OL,8,FProductions - urges large companies to
OL,9,Fhire local talent when working in the
OL,10,FNorth, instead of bringing talent from
OL,11,FLondon.
OL,13,FHEADS creative Liam Heeley said: "I
OL,14,Fthink one of the main reasons why
OL,15,Fpeople book talent from London is
OL,16,Fbecause I think a lot of people
OL,17,Fpresume they're more equipped.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1779829869
OL,3,CThe campaign urging big brands to
OL,4,C'Think North'
OL,6,F"Because there's been a lack of
OL,7,Fopportunity here, so many creatives
OL,8,Fhave took it off their own back to
OL,9,Flearn how to do the craft, learn the
OL,10,Fconnections, learn the industry.
OL,12,F"We really wanted to show in the best
OL,13,Fpossible light, what we've got in the
OL,14,FNorth."
OL,16,FThe campaign launched with a new
OL,17,Fadvert-poem, featuring a young boy who
OL,18,Fasks his grandma "what's a creative?"
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
