PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1779829869
OL,3,CThe campaign urging big brands to
OL,4,C'Think North'
OL,6,FHis question is answered by a range of
OL,7,Fcreatives including actors, musicians,
OL,8,Fpoets, choreographers, tattoo artists,
OL,9,Fphotographers, stylists and
OL,10,Fbroadcasters from Manchester.
OL,12,FThe advert blends grassroots talent
OL,13,Fwith everyday Northern moments, from
OL,14,Fpub chats and family living rooms to
OL,15,Fthe changing skyline.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
