OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1779829869
OL,3,CThe campaign urging big brands to
OL,4,C'Think North'
OL,6,FFilmaker and Jack Fox Productions
OL,7,Ffounder Jack Donohoe said: "It's a
OL,8,Fmoment. It's a moment of almost 100
OL,9,Fcreatives coming together in a room,
OL,10,Fcelebrating what it truly is to be a
OL,11,Fcreative.
OL,13,F"It's a moment to reflect and to open
OL,14,Fa wider conversation about what it is
OL,15,Fto be a creative.
OL,17,F"We should be supporting Northern
OL,18,Ftalent more, especially when companies
OL,19,Fcome here instead of bringing those
OL,20,Fteams with them."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/8
