OL,3,CThe campaign urging big brands to
OL,4,C'Think North'
OL,6,FThe Creative Industries Policy and
OL,7,FEvidence Centre (PEC) states the North
OL,8,Fof England is home to about 23% of the
OL,9,FBritish population and represents
OL,10,Faround 15% of creative industries
OL,11,Femployment.
OL,13,FGreater Manchester's creative
OL,14,Findustries are estimated at around
OL,15,F#1.4bn GVA and more than 48,000 jobs.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/8
