OL,3,CThe campaign urging big brands to
OL,4,C'Think North'
OL,6,FMusician Tabi Gazele who is featured
OL,7,Fin the campaign's launch video said:
OL,8,F"This project is so necessary for the
OL,9,FNorth, just for people themselves to
OL,10,Fknow whose in the community, to know
OL,11,Fwhat world class talent is right here.
OL,13,F"Off the back of this video, I want to
OL,14,Fsee genuine opportunities for
OL,15,Fcreatives. I want impact and for
OL,16,Fpeople to go: I can stay in the North,
OL,17,FI can have a career, I can build
OL,18,Fsomething"
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/8
