OL,3,CThe campaign urging big brands to
OL,4,C'Think North'
OL,6,FThe video features a poem, made up of
OL,7,Fwhat those involved what being a
OL,8,FNorthern creative means to them.
OL,10,FThe poem is passed from person to
OL,11,Fperson, line by line, as a roll call
OL,12,Fof talent across Greater Manchester.
OL,14,FWant more on the issues effecting the
OL,15,FNorth? Our podcast, From the North
OL,16,Fanswers the questions that matter to
OL,17,Four region.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/8
